  <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p>At <strong>Khanqah E Chishtiya - Amreli</strong>, we respect your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how our mobile application (“App”) handles your information. Our app is designed solely to provide access to Islamic religious PDFs for viewing and downloading.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <p>We <strong>do not collect, store, or share</strong> any personal information, including your name, email address, phone number, location, or device data.</p>

  <h2>2. Use of Data</h2>
  <p>Since we do not collect any data, there is no use or processing of personal data by the app.</p>

  <h2>3. PDF Access and Downloads</h2>
  <p>Users can:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>View religious PDFs related to Islamic teachings within the app</li>
    <li>Download these PDFs to their devices for offline use</li>
  </ul>
  <p>These features function entirely on the user's device and do not require any data to be sent to us or third parties.</p>

  <h2>4. Permissions</h2>
  <p>The app may request the following permission:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Device Storage:</strong> To save downloaded PDFs on your phone</li>
  </ul>
  <p>No other permissions are requested. This permission is solely used for enabling offline access to downloaded content.</p>

  <h2>5. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> use third-party analytics, advertising, or tracking tools in the app.</p>

  <h2>6. Children’s Privacy</h2>
  <p>We do not knowingly collect personal data from children under the age of 13. If you believe a child has provided us with personal data, please contact us so we can delete it.</p>

  <h2>7. Data Security</h2>
  <p>Since no data is collected, stored, or transmitted, your information remains private and secure.</p>

  <h2>8. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
  <p>We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page, and we encourage users to review this policy periodically.</p>

  <h2>9. Contact Us</h2>
  <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please contact us:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Email: <a href="mailto:asarafpadarshi@gmail.com">asarafpadarshi@gmail.com</a></li>
